Author: WinonaQuimby
Text: Oh okay, interesting. I was wondering if it's an on/off switch vs a tapering off experience for most people. Thanks for sharing. I hadn't considered the role of body fat percentage, but I've heard similar things about professional female athletes.

Author: littlesunbabe
Text: One month my period just didn’t come. And it still hasn’t. It’s been 6 months. And I’m not even “underweight” technically (only a few lbs away from it though) I am “under fat” though for a women due to a few years of weight training driving it down. I think body fat percentage plays a large roll in loss of period.
